title: 192: Takeaways from Nike's The Opening Camp
itunes:title: 192: Takeaways from Nike's The Opening Camp
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back from "The Opening" to break down what they saw from the best pros and prospects that attended the camp. The guys also debate which current NFL players would be the best option to coach following Von Miller's star-studded pass rush summit this weekend.
